> @Rishith25 do a self review of the changes

@rithviknishad  In my recent commit I have removed the unused `_open`. 
As Tooltip clicks are not supported in mobile view I have done the changes according to this https://github.com/shadcn-ui/ui/issues/86#issuecomment-2241817826 which you have suggested and used the `onMouseEnter` and `onMouseLeave` in `tooltip.tsx` file and handled click Event in `FacilityCard` for mobile view

Is this the required solution for the above issue

Example:
Before:
```.js
verifyUploadFilePresence(fileName: string) {
    cy.wait(2000);
    cy.get("#file-div").scrollIntoView();
    cy.verifyContentPresence("#file-div", [fileName]);
  }
```
After:
```.js
verifyUploadFilePresence(fileName: string) {
    // Replace cy.wait(2000) with intercepting the file upload API call
    cy.intercept('POST', '/api/upload-file').as('fileUpload'); 
    cy.wait('@fileUpload'); // Wait for the file upload request to finish

    cy.get("#file-div").scrollIntoView(); 
    cy.verifyContentPresence("#file-div", [fileName]);
}
```
If this is correct I would like to work on this
